OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FFamilies who have advocated for
OL,7,Fchanges to criminal sentences in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland have spoken of "light
OL,9,Fat the end of the tunnel" after long-
OL,10,Fawaited legislation came to the
OL,11,FStormont.
OL,13,FJustice Minister Naomi Long brought
OL,14,Fthe Sentencing Bill to the assembly as
OL,15,Ffamilies of Lisa Dorrian and Enda
OL,16,FDolan, who have campaigned for decades
OL,17,Ffor reforms to the justice system,
OL,18,Fwatched from the public gallery.
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FThe wide-ranging reforms include a
OL,7,Fnumber of measures that aim to
OL,8,F"strengthen and improve the existing
OL,9,Fframework" for sentencing for crimes,
OL,10,Fincluding raising the maximum sentence
OL,11,Ffor causing death or serious injury by
OL,12,Fdangerous driving from 14 years to 20
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FPeter Dolan, whose son Enda was 18
OL,16,Fwhen he was killed by a drunk driver,
OL,17,Fsaid their decade-long campaign to
OL,18,Fincrease sentences for dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving "has been a rocky road".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]{D@IOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"We have got a wee bit of light at the
OL,7,Fend of the tunnel," he said.
OL,9,F"It's fantastic to get a good debate
OL,10,Fhere today and we have heard from all
OL,11,Fthe different parties and the positive
OL,12,Fcomments from the parties that they're
OL,13,Fin favour of what has been in the
OL,14,FBill."
OL,16,FMs Long said: "I recognised the pain
OL,17,Fthat the Dolan family have felt and
OL,18,Fother families have felt when they've
OL,19,Flost a loved one because of other
OL,20,Fpeople's reckless conduct.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@SO]qD@AOUvD@FO]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"I very much believe that the maximum
OL,7,Fsentence that was available did not
OL,8,Freflect the seriousness of the crime,
OL,9,Fdid not reflect the loss and the harm
OL,10,Fthat it caused."
OL,12,FThe Bill also creates new starting
OL,13,Fpoints on sentences for murder ` 15
OL,14,Fyears where no significant aggravating
OL,15,Ffactors are present and 20 years for
OL,16,Fthe most serious cases.
OL,18,FJoanne Dorrian, whose sister Lisa was
OL,19,F25 when she was last seen alive in
OL,20,F2005, also appeared alongside the
OL,21,FJustice Minister.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FThe Bill will bring in "Charlotte's
OL,7,FLaw?", which aims to reduce the trauma
OL,8,Fexperienced by families of murder
OL,9,Fvictims in so-called "no body" cases
OL,10,Fby creating a statutory aggravator for
OL,11,Ffailure to disclose the location of
OL,12,Fvictims' remains and new sentence
OL,13,Freductions for post-sentence
OL,14,Fdisclosures.
OL,16,FIt will also introduce provisions
OL,17,Fequivalent to Helen's Law in England
OL,18,Fand Wales, requiring parole
OL,19,Fcommissioners to consider failure to
OL,20,Fdisclose the location of victims'
OL,21,Fremains in release decisions.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@EO]qD@VOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FMs Long said the department has worked
OL,7,Fwith families "to look at staged
OL,8,Finterventions" to create "a series of
OL,9,Fincentives for someone who knows where
OL,10,Fthe bodies are to give that
OL,11,Finformation up to the families".
OL,13,F"It is an awful thing to lose a child
OL,14,For a sibling or a friend, and it is a
OL,15,Ftruly awful thing not to have anywhere
OL,16,Fyou can go and actually spend time
OL,17,Fwith them to mark those important
OL,18,Fanniversaries and those times when you
OL,19,Fjust want to reflect on their life,
OL,20,Fthat's another harm being caused to
OL,21,Ffamilies," she said.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@NO]pD@ZOUsD@_O]uD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"It's another trauma they've had to
OL,7,Fbear."
OL,9,FMs Dorrian said Charlotte's law
OL,10,F"really has the potential to change
OL,11,Fthe lives of the families that are
OL,12,Fleft behind".
OL,14,F"It has the potential to find the
OL,15,Fgirls and bring them back, and when we
OL,16,Fget a conviction for Lisa, we then
OL,17,Fhope that Charlotte's law will allow
OL,18,Fthe perpetrator to let us lay Lisa to
OL,19,Frest," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@FO]rD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
