FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FThe Sentencing Bill would introduce a
OL,7,Fstatutory aggravator model for hate
OL,8,Fcrimes amid record levels of racially
OL,9,Fmotivated offences and creates a new
OL,10,Foffence of assaulting a person
OL,11,Fdelivering a public service.
OL,13,FIt will also make provision in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland legislation for
OL,15,Funduly lenient sentences; including a
OL,16,Fvulnerable victim aggravator, where
OL,17,Fthe offender knows or ought reasonably
OL,18,Fto have known the victim was
OL,19,Fvulnerable; and introduce a
OL,20,Fdiscretionary life sentence for repeat
OL,21,Foffenders.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
