FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FSpeaking in the chamber, Ms Long
OL,7,Facknowledged the Bill includes "some
OL,8,Fnovel and unique provisions".
OL,10,FShe said: "I do not believe and have
OL,11,Fnever believed that novel and unique
OL,12,Fshould be weaknesses. Quite to the
OL,13,Fcontrary, they are the purpose of
OL,14,Fdevolution.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@\O]rD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"Importantly, I believe that this Bill
OL,7,Fmakes significant changes that will
OL,8,Fmake a positive difference to the
OL,9,Fpeople we represent, and in particular
OL,10,Fto victims of crime, as well as
OL,11,Fimproving confidence in the criminal
OL,12,Fjustice system and increasing
OL,13,Ftransparency and effectiveness of
OL,14,Fsentencing."
OL,16,FDUP MLA Paul Frew, chairman of the
OL,17,FJustice Committee, noted that many of
OL,18,Fthe proposed measures "have been
OL,19,Finformed by and championed by victims
OL,20,Fand their families", and those will
OL,21,F"be of great interest to the public".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]zD@WOU|D@SO]}D@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,FHe added that the committee have
OL,7,Fsought "information on the deterrence
OL,8,Ffactor of longer sentencing and the
OL,9,Fpotential impact of longer sentencing
OL,10,Fon the prison system".
OL,12,F"This is particularly important as
OL,13,Fmembers have heard that the prison
OL,14,Fpopulation is at an all-time high and
OL,15,Fthe prison service is therefore under
OL,16,Fpressure," he said.
OL,26,@oD@HOUrD@UO]tD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"We are keen, therefore, to see the
OL,7,Fanalysis that has been done on this
OL,8,FBill's possible impact on the prison
OL,9,Fservice and if it will potentially add
OL,10,Fto those existing unprecedented
OL,11,Fpressures."
OL,13,FIn her conclusion to the debate on
OL,14,FMonday, Ms Long said: "We've seen
OL,15,Ftoday how much this does impact people
OL,16,Fin our community, how it actually
OL,17,Faffects people's lives.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]vD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773785475
OL,3,CFamilies 'light at end of the tunnel'
OL,4,Cas tougher sentencing Bill introduced
OL,6,F"What we do here is not just theatre
OL,7,Fand pantomime, it has to be important,
OL,8,Fand legislation is where the rubber
OL,9,Fhits the road.
OL,11,F"So, I think it's taken too long to
OL,12,Fget to this point, but I'm glad that
OL,13,Fwe are now here."
